code: @Override protected SSLSocket configureSocket(SSLSocket sslSocket) throws IOException {     return new TlsFallbackScsvDisabledSSLSocket(sslSocket). }

@Override public void setEnabledCipherSuites(String[] suites) {     List<String> enabledCipherSuites = new ArrayList<>(suites.length).     for (String suite : suites) {         if (!suite.equals(TLS_FALLBACK_SCSV)) {             enabledCipherSuites.add(suite).         }     }     delegate.setEnabledCipherSuites(enabledCipherSuites.toArray(new String[enabledCipherSuites.size()])). }
